        LESS USEFUL BUT FUN TO KNOW

  C-a, C-x            - increment / decrement

  NUMBER: 123 


        SOME ADVANCED STUFF

  C-p [I]             - auto-complete
  C-x [I]             - enter completion mode
  C-v [N]             - enter visual block mode
  m {register}        - save bookmark
  ` {register}        - jump to bookmark
  ``                  - jump back to the previous cursor position
  q {register}        - start recording macro
  q [R]               - stop recording macro
  @ {register}        - play macro


